====================
 SL unit test suite
====================

Configuration
=============

To configure the program suite, use the following commands::

   ./configure
   make

Additionally, the programs can be checked using::

   make check

You can use the additional flag ``-jN`` with ``make`` for parallel
builds.

Running benchmarks
==================

In benchmark directories after ``make`` has succeeded the benchmarking
experiments can be run using::

   make bench

